    "import numpy as np\n",
    "def reject_outliers(data):\n",
    "    m = 2\n",
    "    u = np.mean(data)\n",
    "    print(\"mean is:\", u)\n",
    "    s = np.std(data)\n",
    "    print(\"std is:\", s)\n",
    "    filtered = [e for e in data if (u - 2 * s < e < u + 2 * s)]\n",
    "    print(\"removed:\",np.shape(data)[0] - np.shape(filtered)[0])\n",
    "    return filtered"
